=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
דּבק / dâbaq / daw-bak'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
properly to [[impinge]], that is, [[cling]] or [[adhere]]; figuratively to catch by pursuit: - abide, fast, cleave (fast together), follow close (hard, after), be joined (together), keep (fast), overtake, pursue hard, stick, take.